params.isas: The uint[][] of categoryId and isaIndex. Ex: isas = [ [categoryId, isaIndex], [categoryId, isaIndex] ]

requestInspection().details: Allows the current user (producer) request a inspection.

params.id: the id of a category that receives a vote.
